text: Karimpur may refer to: *Karimpur is a town in Karimpur in the Indian state of West Bengal. *Karimpur I is a town in Karimpur in the Indian state of West Bengal. *Karimpur II is a town in Karimpur in the Indian state of West Bengal. *Karimpur (Vidhan Sabha constituency) is an assembly constituency in the Indian state of West Bengal. *Karimpur Pannadevi College is a College in Nadia district. *Karimpur (Ludhiana West) is a village located in the Ludhiana West tehsil, of Ludhiana district, Punjab.
title: Karimpur (disambiguation)
